    "loadingPattern": "To use in Phaser: copy the specific .png to assets/, add a this.load.spritesheet() or this.load.image() call in BootScene.js, and add to assets/manifest.json.",
    "enemiesNote": "Cozy Farm enemies (slime, bat, ghost) are provided as GIF sequences — you would need to extract frames into a spritesheet PNG to use in Phaser. Alternatively the slime_all.png sheet (720×256) can be sliced.",
    "characterNote": "Cozy Character uses a large merged sheet format (256×1568 per character) — each animation row is a strip within this sheet. Requires careful frame index math when creating Phaser animations."
